{"tid":2130621,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［做香港人好折墮］林奠借疫情限聚禁食延遲選舉，我地可以點反抗？","createTime":"2020-07-29T10:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T11:30:40.000Z","uid":134567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bcf5feb678366e73ed74e13caeb84fe23f2504a","tid":2130621,"uid":134567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:19:32.000Z","msg":"林奠正苦遲遲唔封關，推埋啲擾民又唔治本嘅政策，今日見到好多人要係街邊食飯，真係好嬲，但更嬲嘅係仲有好多人都唔覺得有問題，覺得因為疫情嚴重所以都要逆來順受！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以俾正苦借疫情就可以為所欲為，今日限聚禁食，聽日永續立會，再之後真係唔知會點，一齊集思廣益，點樣係疫情之下反抗，點樣爭取封關同取消免檢！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fbfa30a3e160725e14f259c7bb2949b90274b6","tid":2130621,"uid":6237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"你見成個鐘都冇人覆你<br />\n你就知佢地唔會反抗"},{"pid":"cdb724c83751fa50e2c1b30c335a2053b3790a85","tid":2130621,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"感覺上佢係想罰香港人"},{"pid":"26a66a7d9ae8b6f1e125328ca6c12379837ada75","tid":2130621,"uid":224848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540599-20200729.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540599-20200729.htm&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=765c547a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540599-20200729.htm&h=7a6e9b54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540599-20200729.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n連係廁所食飯都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係政總聽日開翻canteen堂食<br />\n<br />\n唔洗去到外國，我地已經做緊三等公民"}]}